{"tid":2427723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周天行指7.21遇襲孕婦既非證人亦無她的聯絡資料","createTime":"2021-03-01T04:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T06:49:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2af416ebea13307f4996882102d4ef4bb56b1c0e","tid":2427723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"庭上播放一段《立場新聞》直播片段，顯示何桂藍與證人A的受襲過程。證人A供稱，當時看見遇襲女記者身上沒有任何防護裝備，故決定出閘嘗試拉開她，「只係得肉身被打&hellip;&hellip;正常人都會衝出去幫佢」。<br />\n<br />\nA憶述出閘後隨即遭兩至三名白衣男子圍毆，整個過程持續約30至40秒，其間三度被襲，「我只可以用成個身包住嗰女記者，由得佢打落去」。片段顯示，有白衣人向鏡頭方向揮動圓框狀金屬硬物。<br />\n<br />\n施襲白衣男子及後走開，A與女記者退到7-11便利店附近，在對面鴻福堂發現救護員和一名倒臥在地的年輕白衫女子。A發覺到自己正在流血，所以與女記者前去找救護員幫手。<br />\n<br />\n當走到鴻福堂外面，A聽見有店內職員謂「唔好走出嚟喇」，又看見地上女子「攤喺地下冇乜反應」。當時有市民嘗試了解她的情況，但女子仍然閉目，沒有任何反應，「途人好擔心，唔知佢係受傷定受驚」。<br />\n<br />\n法官葉佐文主動詢問控方，該名女子是否證人之一。主控周天行表示該女子並非證人。葉官追問：「係搵唔到佢？」周天行查問後回應謂：「搵唔到呀，法官閣下。」葉官再問：「冇呢位女士嘅資料？資料都冇？」周表示沒有。<br />\n<br />\nA續供稱，現場有一名左手綁有紅絲帶、身穿白色恤衫的男子，一直觀察及拍攝現場情況，「我當時印象個男子係一個指揮嚟嘅」，懷疑該人是指揮、帶隊或「雞頭」角色。A又補充指，「雞頭」原為黑社會用語，意指領頭的人，但因為在不同電影中使用，現已變成流行文化的普通用詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/O7O3UKPGSVC37N7XPZC4WY5YKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FO7O3UKPGSVC37N7XPZC4WY5YKU%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3XQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=4a5b1347\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210301%2FO7O3UKPGSVC37N7XPZC4WY5YKU%2F&h=a7da2d84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210301/O7O3UKPGSVC37N7XPZC4WY5YKU/</a>"},{"pid":"c0fdf4a62bef3361f62f625656f0eee22197e2c1","tid":2427723,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14008&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3XQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=660af576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14008</a><br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️緊急呼籲‼️‼️‼️<br />\n#區域法院第廿八庭 <br />\n#葉佐文法官<br />\n#審訊 [6/25]<br />\n#不是聲援 #白衣暴徒 #元朗黑夜<br />\n#0721元朗 #721唔見人<br />\n案件編號：(已合併)<br />\nDCCC 888/2019<br />\nDCCC 11/2020<br />\nDCCC 734/2020<br />\n<br />\n🚹🚹白衣暴徒🚹🚹<br />\n控罪：<br />\n暴動、串謀有意圖而傷人、有意圖而傷人<br />\n<br />\n主控是 #周天行先生<br />\n高級助理刑事檢控專員(特別職務)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️緊急呼籲‼️‼️‼️<br />\n希望當晚被白衣人打至倒地的年輕 白衣孕婦 (<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190723/s00001/1563890883621/%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E3%80%91%E7%99%BD%E8%A3%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B33%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%B2%92%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E6%B1%82%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%89%E8%83%8E%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00001%2F1563890883621%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B33%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%2583%258E%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%2589&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3XQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=cf15f6ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190723%2Fs00001%2F1563890883621%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%2599%25BD%25E8%25A3%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B33%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%25B2%2592%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2589%2580%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%2583%258E%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%2589&h=2c3f7681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190723/s00001/1563890883621/%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E3%80%91%E7%99%BD%E8%A3%99%E5%A5%B3%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B33%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%B2%92%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2-%E8%A8%BA%E6%89%80%E6%B1%82%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%89%E8%83%8E%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89</a>) 能聯絡律政司/警方落口供甚至出庭作證🙏🏻 <br />\n<br />\n控方指因未能辨認該倒地女士身份，故未能傳召她作供。<br />\n<br />\n直播員又好嬲好嬲，但明白各受害者有其顧慮，如果能鼓起勇氣憶述事發經過指證白衣人劣行當然最好，不願意作證亦可以理解。祝 安康💛<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️‼️緊急呼籲‼️‼️‼️"},{"pid":"9d6c3ed4cf8e88e02296897317267a0f6a517bbd","tid":2427723,"uid":255637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀小牛農場 起曬底仲周街走tim啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a6d1937aa8731ced85102151973006a18a8883","tid":2427723,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d6c3ed4cf8e88e02296897317267a0f6a517bbd","tid":2427723,"uid":255637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀小牛農場 起曬底仲周街走tim啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca4376bbc01d2bfdc7f12b163ea86d3d6347443f","tid":2427723,"uid":131278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"立場姐姐喺另一個庭準備面對國安法控罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\